<measure quantity="9" unit="months">
<num value="9">九</num>月</measure>
<measure quantity="6" unit="days">
<num value="6">六</num>日</measure>
<pc>，</pc>發太皇太後冊寶於大慶殿<pc>，</pc>發皇太後<pc>、</pc>太 妃冊寶於文德殿<pc>，</pc>行禮如儀<pc>。</pc>
