<num value="5">五</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>冊<date notBefore="1086" notAfter="1094">元祐</date>皇後為隆祐太後<pc>，</pc>令所司擇日奉上冊寶<pc>，</pc>時方巡幸<pc>，</pc>不克行禮<pc>；</pc>遙尊韋賢妃為<date notBefore="1119" notAfter="1125">宣和</date>皇後<pc>。</pc>紹興<measure quantity="7" unit="years">
